company_name: 武汉新芯集成电路股份有限公司
title: SPI NOR Flash
base_info: Wide Power Range, Wide Temperature：Full voltage range: 1.65V to 3.6V，-40℃ to +125℃ operating range；High Performance Serial Flash (SPI)：Maximum to 166MHz for fast read operation，Continuous Read 8/16/32/64 Byte Burst Wrap，QPI for Reduced Instruction Overhead，Maximum to 200MHz for DTR clock；Support With Most Flexibility：Provide KGD and RDL，UID and other special customized items，KGD

company_name: 武汉新芯集成电路股份有限公司
title: Known Good Die (KGD)
base_info: 武汉新芯为需要 NOR Flash 定制系统级封装 (SiP) 或多芯片封装 (MCP)的客户提供 Known Good Die (KGD) 解决方案。所有的武汉新芯 SPI NOR 产品都能以 KGD 形式提供；武汉新芯可以提供 RDL (re-Distribution Layer)工艺来满足客户定制化的 pad 布局；定制化的 I/O 数量；对功能、数据保留、cycling 次数等进行完备的测试；专业技术人员将与 KGD 客户一同合作满足他们的特定要求；高效的生产控制和计划体系以确保长期的供应和支持。

company_name: 武汉新芯集成电路股份有限公司
title: SPI NOR Flash
base_info:
•single voltage supply
-voltage: 2.3v to 3.6v
•high performance serial flash (spi)
-maximum to 133mhz for fast read operation
-continuous read 8/16/32/64 byte burst wrap
-qpi for reduced instruction overhead
•flexible memory architecture

•advanced security feature
-128-bit unique id for each device
-3x256-bytes dedicated security area with otp user-lockable bits
